  "text": "TaMYB31-B ORF was amplified using primers TaMYB31-OE-F and TaMYB31-OE-R (containing attB sites) and cloned into the Gateway plant expression vector pB2GW7 to generate p35S:: TaMYB31-B. The transformation of the generated construct into Arabidopsis was performed via A. tumefaciens (strain GV3101) mediated floral-dip method [CITATION_1] . The transgenic seedlings were confirmed by PCR and quantitative RT-PCR.",
